e Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S1-E2-sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B3\",\"beatUid\":\"bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"locationId\":\"L1\",\"locationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"我需要一张基于这个场景，然后背景是太阳花从的中景照片，背景稍微虚化一点\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S1-E2-bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B3\",\"beatUid\":\"bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B3_bac1df.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacterId\":\"C1\",\"connectedCharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"connectedCharacterImage\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocationId\":\"L1\",\"connectedLocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"connectedLocationImage\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\",\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S1-E2-bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B3\",\"beatUid\":\"bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"videoUrl\":\"\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B3_bac1df.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S1-E2-bt48a4b13d352a405f9a0c16b0cd52c819\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S1-E2-B3\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B3_bac1df.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":3407.3847623375223,\"y\":100.61428246858304},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S1-E2-S4\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S1-E2\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\",\"characterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"locationId\":\"L1\",\"locationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S1-E2-bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B4_eb7371.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S1-E2-bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\",\"videoUrl\":\"\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B4_eb7371.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S1-E2-bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompIm