r bright red cloak, and set off toward Grandmother's house.\"}]}]}", "beat_first_frame_history": "{\"history\": {\"S1-E1-B1\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B1_46a5ba.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B1_ab15a9.png\"], \"S1-E1-B2\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B2_467672.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B2_40a012.png\"], \"S1-E1-B3\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B3_821163.png\"], \"S1-E1-B4\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B4_b8eb8e.png\"], \"S1-E1-B5\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B5_c95a56.png\"], \"S1-E1-B6\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B6_f95875.png\"], \"S1-E1-B7\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B7_9bc4c7.png\"], \"S1-E1-B8\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B8_d91a37.png\"], \"S1-E1-B9\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_f30364.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_636aca.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_ee3ae9.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_0d1413.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_6c25e5.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_1428cd.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_7d8e2c.png\"], \"S1-E1-B10\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B10_cf36dc.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B10_bca786.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B10_0f1ff6.png\"], \"S1-E1-B11\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B11_45de27.png\"], \"S1-E2-B1\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_f4ab57.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_432618.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_2977ca.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_7be173.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_76e436.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_e2b325.png\"], \"S1-E2-B2\": [\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B2_252063.png\", \"http://hdvis.tianeo.